_sText:
Created by bigbadDeagle (aka Bonesaw)

I was bored, and decided to make a signature map that I can challenge people in. Just a simple map. 2 Forts, a big open space in the middle, a river, landmines, etc.

Details:
-Landmines in random places of the river
-3 story forts. Bottom, Middle, Roof (both forts the same for each team)
-wall outlining the yard that you can travel on
-breakable steel bar windows
-door frames with prop_door_rotating entities!
-rain
-3d hill skybox

...ENJOY!
